{
  "stem": "4226.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a bit of extra food, plus we had some dry food-- dry food [BACKROUND NOISE] from when we were taken from the synagogue to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went like a long caravan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe was about-- were about 30 carriages.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we were handed food from peasants from the village.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were only two more villages to be passed through.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But no, we -we got-- I remember I got sausages from-- smoked sausages from Romanian peasants, mainly Romanians.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we, we, we could keep it or eat it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, we got extra bread.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in the ghetto, they didn't supply food for the people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody had to have some dry food to keep them going for two weeks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no, no food, like a kitchen, supplies, anything, even tea or coffee.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Of course, there was no-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there was no running water there, just a well and the river.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, they had to build some temporary toilet facilities, which were just along, along the lines of timber, with, with a bit of a fence in between male and female toilets.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It weren't even a hole.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a trench.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And no, no cubicles or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a fence with-- it was a trench with partitions in it, so that people could be separated from one another.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No separation.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just a long--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A long trench for men and a long trench for women.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were close to each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they-- one couldn't see the other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like, they had a sort of a fence between them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But each could see each other inside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they, they guarded it all, all around the ghetto, Hungarian guards.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
